"是 Sylanne 的身份核——一个紧凑的隐向量 。词源上 ben（本，essential）+ vo（我，self），读音对着中文「本我」。 但它最关键的性质，是它在因果链里的位置：": "is Sylanne's identity core — a compact latent vector . Etymologically ben (本, essential) + vo (我, self), pronounced like the Chinese 「本我」 (the id). But its most crucial property is where it sits in the causal chain:",
"引擎对此给了两条可证明的命题：伤疤单调性 恒成立，没有任何治愈机制； 人格不变性 对所有训练步成立。「回不去」因此不是修辞，是定理。": "The engine gives two provable propositions about this: scar monotonicity holds at all times, with no healing mechanism whatsoever; personality invariance holds across every training step. \"No way back\" is therefore not rhetoric — it is a theorem.",
