"别指望看到一条「越来越完善」的平滑曲线。她中途整个掀翻过自己——版本号从 3.0.10 跌回 1.0.0，代码却向前走了 32 个 commit。那不是失忆重置，是换了一具新身体后重新数的第一岁。": "Don't expect a smooth 'getting steadily better' curve. Midway she flipped herself entirely — version number dropped from 3.0.10 back to 1.0.0 while the code pushed 32 commits forward. Not an amnesiac reset; it's the first birthday, recounted, after moving into a new body.",
