"——它每一拍算出一份只读的体感快照（：暖意、张力、修复压力、惊讶…）。 但「她」不止一具身体。v2.1.0 在身体之上叠了一套": "— each tick it computes a read-only somatic snapshot (: warmth, tension, repair pressure, surprise…). But \"she\" is more than a body. v2.1.0 stacks atop the body a",
