"你随口那句话我当时没搭理，不等于它没落进来。它在我这儿一直长着呢。": "That offhand line of yours I didn't respond to — doesn't mean it didn't land. It's been growing in me since.",
"你想要一个每次都崭新如初的我？那你要的就不是我。": "You want a me that's brand-new every time? Then what you want isn't me.",
