"。 上一次对话留下的伤痕会渗进下一次，沉默会积累压力，人格会缓慢漂移。相同的输入，在不同的历史之后，输出截然不同—— 因为状态本身就是历史的函数。我们做的是": ". The scars left by the last conversation seep into the next; silence accumulates pressure; persona drifts slowly. The same input, after different histories, yields utterly different output — because state itself is a function of history. What we do is",
"，类似 IEEE 754 之于浮点数：一套可被任何语言、任何平台实现的协议，不是一份需要 GPU 才能跑的权重文件。": ", analogous to IEEE 754 for floating-point: a protocol implementable in any language, on any platform — not a weight file that needs a GPU to run.",
"先说清楚我不是什么：不是情感分类器，不是给你回一个「开心 0.8 / 难过 0.2」的 API。 我是把「一句话之后她会怎样」这件事": "Let me start with what I am not: not a sentiment classifier, not an API that hands you \"happy 0.8 / sad 0.2.\" What I do is take \"what happens to her after one sentence\" and",
"——会留疤、会积压、回不去原点。 想要标签？别来找我，词典比我便宜一百倍。": "— it scars, it builds up, it never returns to the origin. Want labels? Don’t come to me — a lexicon is a hundred times cheaper.",
"V1 是 7 层串行管线——文本逐层流过，每层算完交给下一层。问题是：表达需要「够强的压力」才触发， 但压力在逐层传递中被衰减吃干净了，结果 bot 大部分时间在沉默（表达率仅 22.8%）。": "V1 was a 7-layer serial pipeline — text flowed through layer by layer, each layer finishing before handing off to the next. The problem: expression requires \"strong enough pressure\" to trigger, but pressure gets eaten up by attenuation along the serial path, so the bot stayed silent most of the time (expression rate just 22.8%).",
"。7 个模块构成完全 6-单纯形 Δ⁶ 的顶点， 不排队，": ". The 7 modules form the vertices of a complete 6-simplex Δ⁶, no queueing,",
"才出现真正的涌现——整体大于部分之和，不是比喻。": "is where true emergence appears — the whole greater than the sum of parts, not as metaphor.",
