"通道用进废退，自动发现对当前人格最要紧的连接。配稳态缩放（Turrigiano 2008）守恒总权重预算。": "Channels strengthen with use and weaken without — automatically discovering the connections that matter most for the current persona. Paired with homeostatic scaling (Turrigiano 2008) to conserve the total weight budget.",
