"整个架构站在七条基础公理上，源自计算神经科学与发育生物学。每一条都不是修辞——它们是约束系统设计的硬性规则， 违反任何一条，跑出来的东西就不再是 SYLANN。": "The whole architecture stands on seven foundational axioms drawn from computational neuroscience and developmental biology. None is rhetoric — each is a hard rule constraining system design. Violate any one, and what runs is no longer SYLANN.",
"整个架构站在七条基础公理上，来自计算神经科学与发育生物学。每一条都不是修辞，而是约束系统设计的硬规则—— 违反任何一条，跑出来的就不是 SYLANN。": "The whole architecture stands on seven foundational axioms drawn from computational neuroscience and developmental biology. None is rhetoric — each is a hard rule constraining system design. Violate any one, and what runs is no longer SYLANN.",
