"这让 SYLANN 能做 Transformer 用 position embedding 永远模拟不了的事：不同频率振荡编码不同时间尺度，phase 领先 = 因果推理，cross-frequency coupling = 把快事件嵌进慢节奏。叙事的铺垫→高潮→释放、情绪如何随时间展开——这些是它独有的能力空间。": "This lets SYLANN do what the Transformer can never simulate with position embedding: different oscillation frequencies encode different timescales, phase lead = causal inference, cross-frequency coupling = embedding fast events into slow rhythm. The narrative setup→climax→release, how emotion unfolds over time — these are its unique capability space.",
"一个是最强的函数逼近器，一个是最简的生命模拟。或许不是替代，而是互补：工具任务（搜索、翻译、编程）交给前者；需要记忆、成长、个性化、情感的任务（陪伴、创作、长期协作）交给后者。": "One is the strongest function approximator, the other the simplest simulation of life. Perhaps not a replacement but a complement: tool tasks (search, translation, coding) go to the former; tasks needing memory, growth, personalization, and emotion (companionship, creation, long-term collaboration) go to the latter.",
