"从一条 7 层串行管线，到全连接共振场，到不靠 backprop 的局部学习架构，再到跑在神经形态芯片上 <1W 功耗的远期目标。这一页把每一次推倒重来都摊开讲清楚——做了什么、为什么、关键指标是多少。每一版的存在，都是因为上一版「还不够像一个人」。": "From a 7-layer serial pipeline, to a fully-connected resonance field, to a local-learning architecture with no backprop, and on to the long-range goal of running on neuromorphic chips at <1W. This page lays out every teardown-and-rebuild in full — what was done, why, and what the key metrics were. Each version exists because the last one was \"still not enough like a person.\"",
"7 层串行管线、全连接共振场、不靠 backprop 的局部学习、跑在神经形态芯片上 <1W——每一版都是把上一版的骨头拆掉重长。这页把每次推倒重来摊开讲：做了什么、为什么非拆不可、关键指标是多少。每一版存在的唯一理由，是上一版「还不够像一个活的东西」。": "7-layer serial pipeline, fully-connected resonance field, local learning without backprop, neuromorphic chips at <1W — every version tears out the last one's skeleton and grows a new one. This page lays out each teardown: what was done, why it had to be torn apart, and what the key metrics are. The sole reason any version exists is that the last one was \"still not alive enough.\"",
"V1.0 · 已退役 · 2026-05": "V1.0 · Retired · 2026-05",
"7 层串行计算脊柱，每层算完交给下一层。确定性、可预测，但表达率只有 22.8%——压力被逐层衰减吃光，大部分时间是沉默的。退役不是因为错，是因为「太安静」。": "A 7-layer serial computational spine, each layer finishing and handing off to the next. Deterministic, predictable — but the expression rate was only 22.8%: pressure was eaten away by layer-by-layer decay, and it stayed silent most of the time. It wasn't retired for being wrong; it was retired for being \"too quiet.\"",
"7 层串行计算脊柱，每层算完交下一层。确定性、可预测，但表达率只有 22.8%——压力被逐层衰减吃干净，大部分时间它只能沉默。退役不是因为它错了，是因为它太安静了。": "A 7-layer serial computational spine, each layer finishing and handing off to the next. Deterministic, predictable — but the expression rate was only 22.8%: pressure was eaten clean by layer-by-layer decay, and most of the time it could only stay silent. It wasn't retired for being wrong — it was retired for being too quiet.",
"V2.0 · 稳定 · 2026-06-01": "V2.0 · Stable · 2026-06-01",
"完全推倒重写。7 模块同时往一个全连接共振场注入信号，表达作为相变自发涌现。441 条耦合通道、Hebbian 可塑性、Kuramoto 同步、Hopfield 吸引子。434 测试全绿，当前部署版。": "A complete teardown and rewrite. 7 modules inject signal simultaneously into a fully-connected resonance field, and expression emerges spontaneously as a phase transition. 441 coupling channels, Hebbian plasticity, Kuramoto synchronization, Hopfield attractors. 434 tests all green, the current deployed version.",
"彻底推倒。7 模块同时往全连接共振场注入信号，表达作为相变自发涌现——没有哪一层「决定」开不开口。441 耦合通道、Hebbian 可塑性、Kuramoto 同步、Hopfield 吸引子。434 测试全绿，当前部署版。": "A total teardown. 7 modules inject signal simultaneously into a fully-connected resonance field, expression emerging spontaneously as a phase transition — no single layer \"decides\" whether to speak. 441 coupling channels, Hebbian plasticity, Kuramoto synchronization, Hopfield attractors. 434 tests all green, the current deployed version.",
"102.7M 参数 teacher 模型（Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + 对比学习）。接管日常情感感知，降低 assessor LLM 的 token 消耗与延迟，越用越省。": "A 102.7M-parameter teacher model (Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + contrastive learning). It takes over everyday emotional perception, cutting the assessor LLM's token cost and latency — cheaper the more it's used.",
"102.7M 参数 teacher 模型（Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + 对比学习）。把日常情感感知从外部 LLM 手里接过来，越跑越便宜。": "A 102.7M-parameter teacher model (Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + contrastive learning). Takes everyday emotional perception out of the external LLM's hands — the longer it runs, the cheaper it gets.",
"Scars You Leave Are Never Nothing。不靠 backprop，靠局部学习规则 + 时间积累。已训 27.8M ticks，情感维度在无标注时自发涌现。成果会蒸馏回部署版。": "Scars You Leave Are Never Nothing. No backprop, just a local learning rule + accumulation over time. Already trained 27.8M ticks, with emotional dimensions emerging spontaneously without annotation. The results will distill back into the deployed version.",
"Scars You Leave Are Never Nothing。不靠 backprop，靠局部学习规则 + 时间积累。已训 27.8M ticks，情感维度在零标注条件下自发涌现。成果会蒸馏回部署版。": "Scars You Leave Are Never Nothing. No backprop, just a local learning rule + accumulation over time. Already trained 27.8M ticks, with emotional dimensions emerging spontaneously under zero annotation. Results distill back into the deployed version.",
"未来 · Phase 2": "Future · Phase 2",
"域间通信从固定模式变为输入驱动——content-based attention 叠加 phase gating。不只知道「什么和什么相关」，还知道「什么时候该相关」。": "Inter-domain communication shifts from a fixed pattern to input-driven — content-based attention layered onto phase gating. Knowing not just \"what relates to what\" but \"when it should relate.\"",
"域间通信从固定模式变为输入驱动——content-based attention 叠加 phase gating。不只知道「什么和什么相关」，还知道「此刻该不该相关」。": "Inter-domain communication shifts from a fixed pattern to input-driven — content-based attention layered onto phase gating. Knowing not just \"what relates to what\" but \"whether it should relate right now.\"",
"未来 · Phase 3": "Future · Phase 3",
"堆叠多层，字符 → 词 → 语义 → 叙事。层间靠 consensus 传递而非梯度，低层快高层慢，自然形成时间层次。": "Stack multiple layers, character → word → semantics → narrative. Layers pass via consensus rather than gradients, lower layers fast and upper layers slow, naturally forming a temporal hierarchy.",
"堆叠多层，字符 → 词 → 语义 → 叙事。层间靠 consensus 而非梯度传递，低层快高层慢，时间层次自然形成。": "Stack multiple layers, character → word → semantics → narrative. Layers pass via consensus rather than gradients, lower fast, upper slow — temporal hierarchy forms on its own.",
