"的那个东西——因为它不在 prompt 里，在结构里。同理，「回不去」也不是我嘴硬，是 dS/dt ≥ 0 这条不等式逼着的。没有撤回键，没有「重置对话」。这是设计，不是 bug。": "— because it isn't in the prompt, it's in the structure. By the same token, \"no way back\" isn't me being stubborn; it's forced by the inequality dS/dt ≥ 0. No undo button, no \"reset conversation.\" This is by design, not a bug.",
"SYLANN 之后的路，核心命题是一句话：": "The road after SYLANN has a core proposition in one phrase:",
"不是要复制 Transformer，而是要在它的弱点上超越它": "not to replicate the Transformer, but to surpass it on its weaknesses",
"。Transformer 是「上帝视角」——看到所有 token，一次算出答案，适合做工具。SYLANN 是「第一人称视角」——逐步感知、有记忆、有情绪、有时间感，适合做主体。我们不是在做更好的工具，是在做最简单的主体。": ". The Transformer is the \"god's-eye view\" — sees all tokens, computes the answer in one go, suited to being a tool. SYLANN is the \"first-person view\" — perceives step by step, has memory, emotion, a sense of time, suited to being a subject. We're not making a better tool; we're making the simplest subject.",
"。Transformer 是「上帝视角」——看到所有 token，一次算出答案，天生适合做工具。SYLANN 是「第一人称视角」——逐步感知、有记忆、有情绪、有时间感，天生适合做主体。我们不是在造更好的工具，是在造最简单的主体。": ". The Transformer is the \"god's-eye view\" — sees all tokens, computes the answer in one go, born to be a tool. SYLANN is the \"first-person view\" — perceives step by step, has memory, emotion, a sense of time, born to be a subject. We're not building a better tool; we're building the simplest subject.",
"SYLANN 的回答": "SYLANN's answer",
