"全对全注意力": "all-to-all attention",
"phase-gated O(D²)，D≪n · 稀疏 WTA": "phase-gated O(D²), D≪n · sparse WTA",
"Phase 1 已经在 V3 里跑（基础验证）。后面五个是路线图。": "Phase 1 is already running in V3 (basic validation). The five after are the roadmap.",
"Phase 1 · 进行中": "Phase 1 · in progress",
"证明 sequential predictive coding + three-factor Hebbian 能学会语言和情感。混合训练 80% 纯预测 + 20% reward-modulated。成功指标：MAE < 0.1。": "Prove that sequential predictive coding + three-factor Hebbian can learn language and emotion. Mixed training of 80% pure prediction + 20% reward-modulated. Success metric: MAE < 0.1.",
"域间通信从固定模式变输入驱动：": "Inter-domain communication goes from fixed pattern to input-driven:",
"。content-based attention 叠加 phase gating——既知道什么和什么相关，又知道什么时候该相关。指标：动态 CFC 比固定 CFC 好 15%+。": ". Content-based attention layered onto phase gating — knowing both what relates to what and when it should relate. Metric: dynamic CFC beats fixed CFC by 15%+.",
"堆叠多层：Sensory（字形/字频）→ Lexical（词义/搭配）→ Semantic（语义/情感）→ Narrative（叙事/逻辑）。层间靠 consensus 传递不靠梯度，低层快高层慢。指标：处理 100K token 无性能退化。": "Stack multiple layers: Sensory (glyph/frequency) → Lexical (meaning/collocation) → Semantic (semantics/emotion) → Narrative (narrative/logic). Layers pass via consensus not gradients, lower fast and upper slow. Metric: no performance degradation processing 100K tokens.",
"第 15 个 Memory Domain，不做 WTA 而是队列式存储。高 surprise 时写入 consensus 快照，其他域通过 CFC 读取，容量 7±2 槽。压缩的关键信息，不是整个 context window。指标：通过简单推理测试。": "A 15th Memory Domain, doing queue-based storage instead of WTA. On high surprise it writes a consensus snapshot, other domains read via CFC, capacity 7±2 slots. Compressed key information, not the whole context window. Metric: passes simple reasoning tests.",
"用 oscillation 做时间推理：phase alignment = 同时性、phase sequence = 因果（A 领先 B 则 A 可能致 B）、cross-frequency coupling = 细节嵌入大纲。应用：音乐、叙事、情绪动力学、对话 timing。这是 position embedding 永远模拟不了的。": "Use oscillation for temporal reasoning: phase alignment = simultaneity, phase sequence = causality (A leading B means A may cause B), cross-frequency coupling = detail embedded in outline. Applications: music, narrative, emotional dynamics, conversational timing. This is what position embedding can never simulate.",
"Loihi / TrueNorth。局部学习无需 backprop → 无需存激活和梯度；event-driven → 只有活跃 cell 耗能。指标：单芯片跑完整 SYLANN，功耗 <1W，约 10000× 能效比。": "Loihi / TrueNorth. Local learning needs no backprop → no storing activations and gradients; event-driven → only active cells consume power. Metric: a single chip running full SYLANN at <1W, about 10000× energy efficiency.",
"WTA 稀疏性让每 tick 仅 ~10% cells 激活。同一套局部规则，靠堆 domain / cell / 维度撑到 GPT-4 级。": "WTA sparsity activates only ~10% of cells per tick. The same local rule, scaled to GPT-4 class by stacking domains / cells / dimensions.",
