"CHANGELOG 很长，这里只挑里程碑。从 2026-05-29 第一个 preview 到现在，不到一个月推倒重来好几次——这种迭代节奏，只有「没有用户、可以随便拆」的项目才敢有。": "The CHANGELOG is long; here we pick only milestones. From the first preview on 2026-05-29 to now, it's been torn down and rebuilt several times in under a month — an iteration pace only a project with \"no users, free to tear apart at will\" would dare.",
"不到一个月，从 preview 干到 v2.0.0 正式版，中间 a1→a4 改了四次。没人用，所以敢拆。这不是不负责任，是把「在有用户的项目上绝对不敢做的实验」全挪到这边来做。": "Under a month from preview to v2.0.0, with a1→a4 reworked four times in between. Nobody's using it, so it dares to be torn apart. This isn't irresponsibility; it's moving all the \"experiments you'd never dare run on a project with users\" over here.",
"先把全貌摆出来。这条线从 V1 一直拉到远期的神经形态部署——实心节点是已经落地或正在跑的，空心节点还只活在脑子里。V1 那个节点标着": "Let's lay out the full picture first. This line stretches from V1 all the way to the long-term neuromorphic deployment — solid nodes are already landed or running, hollow nodes still only live in the mind. The V1 node is marked",
"已退役": "retired",
"，但我没舍得从历史里删它，因为它死的方式精确地定义了 V2 该怎么活。": ", but I couldn't bring myself to delete it from the history — because the way it died precisely defined how V2 should live.",
"。V1 死了，但 V1 教会了 V2 该怎么活。名字最后那个 e 一直没变——": ". V1 died, but V1 taught V2 how to live. That e at the end of the name never changed —",
"堆叠多层，字符 → 词 → 语义 → 叙事。层间靠 consensus 而非梯度传递，低层快、高层慢，时间层次自然形成。": "Stack multiple layers, character → word → semantics → narrative. Layers pass via consensus rather than gradients, lower fast, upper slow — temporal hierarchy forms naturally.",
"lite 档，500 ticks × 10 repeats，统计检验。这些数字是架构换来的，不是调参调出来的。": "lite tier, 500 ticks × 10 repeats, statistical testing. These numbers came from swapping the architecture, not from tuning knobs.",
"的 teacher 模型，架构是 Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + 对比学习的组合。它在本地处理日常情感感知，把昂贵的 LLM 调用频率往下压。": "teacher model, its architecture a blend of Mamba SSM + MoE + Multi-scale ConvStem + VAE + contrastive learning. It handles everyday emotional perception locally, pushing down the frequency of expensive LLM calls.",
"看日期就知道了——不到一个月，从 preview 干到 v2.0.0 正式版，中间 a1→a4 改了四次。没人用，所以敢拆。这不是不负责任，是把「在有用户的项目上绝对不敢做的实验」全挪到这边来做。": "Look at the dates — under a month from preview to v2.0.0, with a1→a4 reworked four times in between. Nobody's using it, so it dares to be torn apart. This isn't irresponsibility; it's moving all the \"experiments you'd never dare run on a project with users\" over here.",
