"。词源上 ben（本，essential）+ vo（我，self），读音对着中文「本我」。 但它最关键的性质，是它在因果链里的位置：": ". Etymologically ben (essential) + vo (self), echoing the Chinese for 'the essential self.' But its key property is its place in the causal chain:",
