"对所有训练步成立。「回不去」因此不是修辞，是定理。": "holds for all training steps. So 'can't go back' isn't rhetoric, it's a theorem.",
"一道伤疤不会突然消失，它沿着固定的时间线衰减——但永远走不到「从未发生」。 RAW 阶段的 alpha 调制最强（信号被放大约 2×，制造过敏感）；越往后影响越小， 可即便 FADED，它仍在那里，只是声音很轻。这是一条单向的路。": "A scar doesn't vanish suddenly; it decays along a fixed timeline — but never reaches 'never happened.' The RAW stage has the strongest alpha modulation (signal amplified ~2×, creating hypersensitivity); the influence shrinks over time, but even when FADED it's still there, just quiet. This is a one-way road.",
