"：在所有扰动下守恒的那个东西。": ": the thing conserved under every perturbation.",
"通俗讲：拓扑学只关心「怎么折腾都不变」的性质。一个甜甜圈，你捏它、揉它、拉长它， 只要不撕开、不补洞，它「有一个洞」这件事就不变——这个「洞数」就是拓扑不变量。 人格在这套系统里扮演的就是这个角色：日常对话像在揉捏这块面团，状态在剧烈起伏， 但有": "In plain terms: topology only cares about properties that 'survive any deformation.' Take a donut — pinch it, knead it, stretch it; as long as you don't tear it or fill the hole, the fact that it 'has one hole' never changes. That 'hole count' is a topological invariant. Persona plays that role here: everyday conversation kneads the dough, the state swings wildly, but a",
"某个守恒量": "certain conserved quantity",
"穿过所有这些扰动，岿然不动。那个守恒量，就是「她还是她」。": "passes through all those perturbations, unmoved. That conserved quantity is 'she is still her.'",
"人格活在微分算子": "Persona lives in the kernel space",
